<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>名人 - 人物</title><link>https://siftrss.com/f/LbvpaQbPYJQ</link><description>来自人物的最新名人新闻、采访和故事。</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 29 Mar 2026 01:18:48 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>泰格·伍兹酒后驾车被捕后首次露面</title><link>https://people.com/tiger-woods-seen-for-first-time-after-leaving-jail-for-dui-arrest-photo-11936604</link><description>这名职业高尔夫球手在 3 月 27 日发生车祸后被指控酒后驾车造成财产损失并拒绝接受合法测试&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://people.com/thmb/qs2gv5DvLMvU-mjvJfg31_qpM1E=/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():format(jpeg)/Tiger-Woods-Martin-County-Jail-032826-0b3ab797483b4c6391a953def7d956f0.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Mar 2026 14:36:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://people.com/tiger-woods-seen-for-first-time-after-leaving-jail-for-dui-arrest-photo-11936604</guid></item><item><title>约瑟夫·杜加尔 (Joseph Duggar) 因猥亵儿童指控被捕后，他的监狱电话和唯一访客被曝光</title><link>https://people.com/joseph-duggars-prison-calls-sole-visitor-revealed-after-child-molestation-arrest-11936592</link><description>这位前真人秀明星于 3 月 18 日因猥亵儿童罪被捕，此后一直被关押在阿肯色州监狱中。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://people.com/thmb/OXCS7HV6kczzJxfYvFHP3WJZWh8=/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():format(jpeg)/Joseph-Duggar-mugshot-031826-9566df9dce63463086e311816b99aac1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Mar 2026 13:17:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://people.com/joseph-duggars-prison-calls-sole-visitor-revealed-after-child-molestation-arrest-11936592</guid></item><item><title>布兰妮·斯皮尔斯 (Britney Spears) 被捕三周后重返 Instagram，与 19 岁的儿子杰登 (Jayden) 分享视频</title><link>https://people.com/britney-spears-shares-video-son-returns-instagram-after-arrest-11936218</link><description>“谢谢你们的支持……与家人和朋友共度时光真是一件幸事！！！”她在标题中写道&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://people.com/thmb/bAaadcE15Yy7z9tEsgpJIN45Rls=/filters:no_upscale(